          "defaultSubject": "Leopoly OMS - Password Reset",
          "defaultHtmlTemplate": "[#setting url_escaping_charset=\"UTF-8\"]\n<h1>Request to change your LeoShape OMS password.</h1>\n\n<p>You have requested to change your password.</p>\n\n<h2>If you did not make this request, please immediately contact our support team.</h2>\n\n<p>If you want to proceed with changing your password, please click on the link below:</p>\n\n<p>\n  <a href=\"${fusionauth_url}/password/change/${changePasswordId}?client_id=${(application.oauthConfiguration.clientId)!''}&tenantId=${user.tenantId}\">Reset your password</a>\n</p>\n\n- Leopoly\n",
          "defaultTextTemplate": "[#setting url_escaping_charset=\"UTF-8\"]\nRequest to change your LeoShape OMS password.\n\nYou have requested to change your password. If you did not make this request, please immediately contact our support team.\n\nIf you want to proceed with changing your password, please click on the link below:\n\n${fusionauth_url}/password/change/${changePasswordId}?client_id=${(application.oauthConfiguration.clientId)!''}&tenantId=${user.tenantId}\n\n- Leopoly\n"
        }
      }
    },
