          "defaultTextTemplate": "Your LeoShape OMS account has been created!\n\nPlease click the link below to set up your first password:\n\n${fusionauth_url}/password/change/${changePasswordId}?client_id=${(application.oauthConfiguration.clientId)!''}&tenantId=${user.tenantId}\n\nYou will soon receive information about getting started with LeoShape OMS.\n\n- Leopoly\n"
