          "defaultHtmlTemplate": "<h1>Welcome to ${requestData.customerName}!</h1>\n\n<p>Your account has been added to <b>${requestData.customerName}</b>.</p>\n\n<p>You can now access the application at:</p>\n\n<p>\n  <a href=\"${requestData.applicationUrl}\">${requestData.applicationUrl}</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>If you have any questions, please contact your administrator.</p>\n\n- Leopoly\n",
